	   <tr><td colspan=2>Rules of the game on Haste: You are allowed one permanent haste Item, if you have more than one on (silly you) the higher haste item will overide.&nbsp;&nbsp;Permanent haste items such as Mitheral 2h sword, FBSS, sash of the dragon borne do stack with either one haste spell or bard song, dat's it.  So if ya got say a FBSS (haste 25% or so) and Analiya's Quickening (40% haste?) they stack for a total haste effect of 65%.  Which can make a properly equiped paladin and buzz saw of outlandish proportions. Check me out in a FBSS and a speed spell wielding an Arbitter's Combine Greatsword (30/43 2h +15 wis)sometime, Things die quickly.<br><br>Anyone on Prexus have some DW armor to sell? tell me in game.<br>&nbsp;<br>Arcturion Al`Dragoran<br>Paladin Extraordinare<br><br>Luuke <br>Ubermonk <br><br>Stasis<br>Prexus Server<br></td></tr>
